"Enemy on the 3rd Table":
"I need your help! I have to pick a design
for the table we're going to have at the
venue, but I can't think of anything!
All the ideas I come up with are things
we've done before!
There's no novelty there!
I need a wacky design that nobody's
ever seen before. Can you let me know
if you think of anything?
※Target Lv. 1+ enemies"
